reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Toiletry Bag for the price
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the BAGSMART Toiletry Bag for Men and it has quickly become my go-to travel companion. This bag is well designed, well-made, and perfect for organizing all of my toiletries during international travel.One of the standout features of this bag is the high-quality zipper. It's extremely easy to open and close, even when the bag is full. This is a welcome change from other toiletry bags I've used in the past where the zipper often gets stuck or is difficult to use. The zipper on this bag is smooth and reliable.Another great feature is that the bag is water-resistant, which gives me peace of mind when traveling with liquids. It's also really easy to clean, which is essential for a toiletry bag that will see a lot of use. The material is durable and feels like it will last for many trips to come.I also appreciate the solid handle on this bag. It makes it easy to carry, even when it's fully loaded. The handle is well-padded and comfortable to hold, which is especially important when you're carrying a heavy bag through the airport or to your hotel room.Finally, the internal organizing slots are simple and effective. They keep all of my toiletries neatly organized and easy to access. I don't have to dig through a jumble of products to find what I need, which saves me time and hassle.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect toiletry bag for travel and work
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a toiletry bag mainly for work since I am on shift for 24-48 hours a day. This is great to put all my needed items in. I love the little mesh pockets in the main compartment to hold my contact lens holder or hair ties.I also really like it has another main pocket that is waterproof (it has a plastic like lining inside.) It could definitely fit one of those microfiber quick drying towels. I have a size large of those and it fits rolled up in there so I really like that feature if I needed it for travel.It's just really well built and I also like the large handle attached so I can hang it up in my locker as well or on a hook in the bathroom. Great buy and can't think of any complaints. :)
